dcterms:description: Zadoff-Chu sequences are used in synchronization signals in 4G LTE and 5G NR, known for their constant amplitude zero autocorrelation (CAZAC) property, which ensures less distortion when passed through amplifiers and maintains low noise levels during correlation.
dcterms:title: Zadoff-Chu (ZC) sequences
